    "synopsis": "Kal Jerico's debts finally catch up with him when the crime boss Nemo forces him into a bounty that sounds too clean to be honest. The target leads back to Cardinal Crimson, a Redemptionist demagogue with a crusade to protect and a newcomer to silence before old secrets can ruin him. Kal, Scabbs, Yoland and the metal mastiff Wotan stumble from contract work into mass-execution politics, where every escape route costs someone else blood. Mid-trilogy Necromunda action-comedy with a sharper religious-thriller bite.",
